These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
House: tower, palace, art-deco, townhouse, colonial, ranch-style, farmhouse
7 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, poker, go, chess, billiard, whist
There are 7 different nationalities: nigerian, australian, malaysian, spanish, argentine, colombian, thai
 1. the colonial house is on the far left##1
 2. the australian is on the left of the tower house##1
 3. the thai is between the person playing monopoly and the person playing canasta##2
 4. the townhouse house is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the palace house##1
 6. the tower house is the thai##1
 7. the person playing go is between the spanish and the colonial house##2
 8. the argentine is on the left of the colombian##1
 9. the colombian is on the left of the nigerian##1
10. the farmhouse house is the person playing poker##1
11. the person playing billiard is the townhouse house##1
12. the farmhouse house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
13. the nigerian is the person playing chess##1
14. the ranch-style house is between the malaysian and the thai##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| House   | colonial | tower     | ranch-style | palace | townhouse | farmhouse  | art-deco  |
| Game   | canasta  | go        | monopoly  | whist     | billiard   | poker       | chess   |
| Nationality         | australian   | thai | spanish    | malaysian  | argentine | colombian | nigerian |

