.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: october, december, april, july, november, february, august
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: adventure, mystery, animation, spy, documentary, superhero, disaster
The people have 7 different jobs:  journalist, pilot, manager, musician, writer, engineer, scientist
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the pilot##1
 2. the person watching documentary movies is the person watching documentary movies##1
 3. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 4. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the journalist##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is the musician##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person watching disaster movies and the scientist##2
 8. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
10. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the writer##1
11. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
12. the journalist is the person who's birthday is in december##1
13. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
14. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the engineer##1
15. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
16. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Birthday   | february | august      | july     | october  | november | april | december |
