13. the american is the doctor##1
14. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1
15. the entrepreneur is on the far right##1
16. the manager is between the malaysian and the person driving the motorbike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |  7   |
| Job   | nurse | designer      | doctor | project-manager     | librarian     | manager   | entrepreneur |
| Nationality       | spanish    | chinese | american    | polish | thai     | italian | malaysian |
| Transport        | taxi    | bike | jet-ski    | helicopter    | motorbike | scooter | snowmobile |

